summary: Curious, driven and dynamic geophysicist with a passion for innovation. Coming from a background of exploration geophysics and seismology, I am now leading a team of innovation engineers working on active and passive seismic technologies for near-surface characterization (infrastructure, renewables). My main interest is in the application of novel technologies in a practical and commercially feasible way to do things better/smarter/faster. I get most energy from connecting (technical) ideas and people. Also, I am passionate about diversity & inclusion (currently advisor EAGE Women in Geoscience & Engineering) and connecting people within our industry (Young IRO board member).
